{
  "stem": "22174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't ever do that again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You want to get killed?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, anyway, so that was the end of that job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I-- until I got [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] recuperated from the dislocation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I worked all sorts of jobs where I could get, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was a kind of a war, a war situation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A civil war situation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, I once had a job for a day in a cemetery, a Jewish cemetery, outside Haifa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] dug around the trees, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next morning there was a funeral of some Jewish high official or so, you know, from the union, I think.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so in one of the-- probably in one of the woods that I made there, there was a bomb.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a bomb in there, and this to be exploded from about half a mile away or so from under a tree.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, fortunately, they found it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was found before it was exploded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was a very hostile situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On the other hand, in some parts of the cities, you know, Jews and Arabs were living together peacefully.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, it was very-- it wasn't ambiguous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not always.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The road were very-- the roads were very insecure, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Buses were often attacked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, as I said before, we had to drive to work to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, we drove to work with iron-- with, yeah, metal plates on the sides of the trucks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the British played a very-- a very ambiguous political game, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried to play one against the other, like they usually do, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
